criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Intracranial unruptured aneurysms confirmed by digital subtraction angiography DSA, CT
             angiography or MR angiography (MRA);

          2. The maximum size of unruptured aneurysm ≤5mm;

          3. Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

        1.Patients with severe systemic disorders and expected life span less than one year;
        2.Pregnant or lactating women.
